code: @Override protected Class<?> resolveFallbackIfPossible(String className, ClassNotFoundException ex) throws IOException, ClassNotFoundException {     // Else, propagate the ClassNotFoundException.     if (this.codebaseUrl == null) {         throw ex.     }     return RMIClassLoader.loadClass(this.codebaseUrl, className). }
@Override protected ClassLoader getFallbackClassLoader() throws IOException {     return RMIClassLoader.getClassLoader(this.codebaseUrl). }
